    - "functools.update_wrapper.__code__.co_argcount == 4 — update_wrapper(wrapper, wrapped, assigned=WRAPPER_ASSIGNMENTS, updated=WRAPPER_UPDATES) takes 4 positional-or-keyword arguments; co_argcount is 4. Verified with Python 3.14.3."
